      %p
        This template is written entirely in
        %strong HTML5
        and
        = succeed "." do
          %strong CSS3
        The photos shown in this template were taken by me. You can view more free CSS3 web templates
        = succeed "." do
          %a{:href => "http://www.css3templates.co.uk"} here
      %p
        This template is a fully documented 5 page website, with an
        %a{:href => "examples.html"} examples
        page that gives examples of all the styles available with this design. There is also a working PHP contact form on the contact page. All of the photos were taken by me - use as you wish.
    - else
      %h3
        = flash[:notice]
      - auth = current_vi_employee_authentication.authentication
      - if auth
        %h5
          Congratulations..! You have connected with facebook apps. You Don't  need to connect again.
        - if @nxt_upcoming_birthdays.present?
          %h4
            List of Recently upcoming birthday on facebook...

          %table{:style => "width:100%"}
            %tr
              %th{:style => 'text-align:center'}
                fb image
              %th{:style => 'text-align:center'}
                Name
              %th{:style => 'text-align:center'}
                BithDate
              %th{:style => 'text-align:center'}
                Fb Profile URl
            - @nxt_upcoming_birthdays.each do |friend|
              %tr
                %td{:style => 'text-align:center'}
                  = link_to image_tag(@graph.get_picture(friend["id"])),friend["link"],:target => "_blank"
                %td{:style => 'text-align:center'}
                  = friend["name"]
                %td{:style => 'text-align:center'}
                  = friend["birthday"]
                %td
                  = friend["link"]
        - else
          %h4
            = flash[:message]
        - end
      - else
        %p
          if you want to use automated birthday wishing for facebook friends. Please connect with facebook app.
          Click On Use FB APP at top menu.
